data.description: Fantastic Royal Troon Gated Community right off Dayton Valley Road, and just minuted away from shopping, the USA Parkway, Lake Tahoe, Carson City, and Reno. Your dollar goes further in Dayton, and this will be evident with this well appointed and nicely upgraded must see home. This is an extremely popular nearly new open concept 3 bedroom 2 Bath home with a gorgeous backdrop to BLM land and wide open views of the Sierra Nevada mountain ranges and complete backyard privacy which is rare in a subdivision. Welcome to your dream home! This meticulously crafted residence by Silverado Builders is a gem in our community. Here's why this property stands out:  Exterior Elegance: Admire the upgraded 2-tone stucco and rock exterior, showcasing the exceptional attention to detail that sets this home apart. Scenic Views and Privacy: Enjoy the breathtaking backdrop of BLM land and wide-open views of the mountain ranges. Experience complete backyard privacy, a rare find in a subdivision setting. Family-Friendly Layout: This open-concept 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom layout is perfect for families. The spacious design allows for versatility and comfortable living. Incredible Value: Your dollar goes further in Dayton, and this home exemplifies the value you seek. Well-appointed and upgraded, this property offers a combination of luxury and affordability.  Community Favorite: Regarded as one of the most popular homes built by Silverado in this community, this residence is a testament to quality and style. Move-In Ready: Immaculate condition and move-in ready – start living your dream without the hassle of renovations or repairs.  Act Fast!: Homes of this caliber are in high demand. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this highly sought-after property your own. It will not last long!  Schedule your private tour today and envision the life that awaits you in this exceptional Dayton home. Make your move before someone else claims this rare piece of paradise!
